quran[8{c,v,t}:
10,7,"haqeeqat yeh hai ke jo log hum se milnay ki tawaqqa nahi rakhtay aur duniya ki zindagi hi par raazi aur mutmaen ho gay hain, aur jo log hamari nshanyon se ghaafil hain"
10,8,unn ka aakhri thikana jahannum ho ga unn buraiyon ki Padaash mein jin ka Iktisab woh ( apne is ghalat aqeday aur ghalat tarz amal ki wajah se ) karte rahay
10,9,"aur yeh bhi haqeeqat hai ke jo log imaan laaye ( yani jinhon ne unn sadaqaton ko qubool kar liya jo is kitaab mein paish ki gayi hain ) aur naik aamaal karte rahay inhen unn ka rab unn ke imaan ki wajah se seedhi raah chalaye ga, Nemat bharijannaton mein un ke neechay nhrin behain gi"
10,10,"wahan un ki sada yeh hogi ke “pak hai to ae khuda,"" unn ki dua yeh hogi ke “slamtiho"" aur un ki har baat ka khtama is par hoga ke “sari tareef Allah rab alaalmin hi ke liye hai """
10,11,agar kahin Allah logon ke sath bura maamla karne mein bhi itni hi jaldi karta jitni woh duniya ki bhalai mangnay mein jaldi karte hain to un ki mohlat amal kabhi ki khatam kar di gayi hoti ( magar hamara yeh tareeqa nahi hai ) is liye hum unn logon ko jo hum se milnay ki tawaqqa nahi rakhtay unn ki sar kashi mein bhatakne ke liye chhُot day dete hain
10,12,"ensaan ka haal yeh hai ke jab is par koi sakht waqt aata hai to kharray aur baithy aur letey hum ko pukaarta hai, magar jab hum is ki museebat taall dete hain to aisa chal nikalta hai ke goya is ne kabhi apne kisi buray waqt par hum ko puraka hi nah tha is terhan hadd se guzar jaane walon ke liye un ke kartoot khushnuma bana diye gay hain"
10,13,"logo, tum se pehlay ki qomon ko ( jo apne apne zamana mein brsr urooj theen ) hum ne halaak kar diya jab unhon ne zulm ki rawish ikhtiyar ki aur unn ke rasool unn ke paas khُli khُli nishanain le kar aeye aur unhon ne imaan laa kar hi nah diya is terhan hum mujrimon ko un ke juraim ka badla diya karte hain"
10,14,ab un ke baad hum ne tum ko zameen mein un ki jagah di hai taakay dekhen tum kaisay amal karte ho
